  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Enable ZIP utility in CI by adding pipeline-utility-steps plugin to Jenkins CI pipeline</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Updates</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update bash&gt;alpine on liferay-dxp</li>\n<li>Update node&gt;alpine on database-service<a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/dxp-cloud/latest/en/platform-services/backup-service/backup-service-overview.html#configuring-the-schedule-via-the-console\">.</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Prevent submitting empty secret variable</li>\n<li>Fixed missing validation when filling required field with only blank spaces for Secrets</li>\n</ul>"
      },
